<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="1400">5.2. Setting up stock for listings</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Decide whether to automatically end listings and adjust their quantity to the net stock in the <strong>Setup » Listings » Stock</strong> menu. Furthermore, select the warehouse which should be used for listings. Note the specifications of the market concerning the termination of listings and legal regulations.</p>
</div>
<div class="admonitionblock important">
<table>
