<li>
<p>Go to <strong>Data » API log » Tab: API log</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Select the <strong>ItemListingControllerHood</strong> option or the <strong>LeaveFeedback</strong> option from the <strong>Process</strong> drop-down list.</p>
