<h2 id="5100">20. Matching data with the import tool</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Use the import tool in the <strong>Data » Import</strong> menu to exchange data between plentymarkets and Hood. Listing data can be imported into plentymarkets with the <a href="/en/data/importing-data/sync-types/elasticsync-market-listing">Market listing</a> import type.</p>
